asset.title: 2015 O'Neill Coldwater Classic Teaser
asset.description:
O’NEILL COLDWATER CLASSIC RETURNS TO STEAMER LANE OCT. 14-18
The O’Neill Coldwater Classic at Steamer Lane returns as stop #30 on the 2015 World Surf League (WSL) Men’s Qualifying Series (QS). A three-decade long annual Santa Cruz tradition, this year’s event boasts a $50,000 prize purse and 1,500 points up for grabs amongst 96 surfers hoping to qualify for the 2016 World Tour. #ONeillCWC
